    p GhostTrain is a mock router library for serving mock data statically. Leveraging the same API as <a href="http://expressjs.com">Express</a>, GhostTrain allows developers to send mock requests to GhostTrain rather than making HTTP requests to a server, for development, testing and demos. Run in a browser, in node, and take development to the next level.
